Interface ParticipantObjectIdType

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface ParticipantObjectIdType extends CodedValueType
The Participant Object ID Type describes the identifier that is contained in Participant Object ID. Codes from coded terminologies and implementation defined codes can also be used.
